    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline facilitated by six individual throttle bodies. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the double VANOS unit has been fully rebuilt, and a comprehensive rod bearing service was recently completed with treated shells. The chassis is exceptionally rigid, featuring proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a precision-aligned suspension utilizing Bilstein PSS10 coilover dampers. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The exterior paint retains its deep factory depth with no discernible swirling, while the undercarriage remains free of any corrosion or fluid seepage. This is a turn-key, mechanically synchronized masterpiece for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 44500.0,
