    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in true showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features the original factory paint, protected by a multi-layer professional ceramic coating that yields a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Step inside to an interior that remains indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery is supple and matte, with no bolster wear or creasing, and every digital display and switch operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete, chronologically organized service binder documenting every fluid flush and inspection performed at certified intervals. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, the transmission shifts are imperceptible, and the undercarriage is free of any road grime or oxidation. Riding on fresh, high-performance tires mounted to flawless alloy wheels with zero curb rash, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a turn-key, investment-grade example.",
