      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle in exemplary, showroom-standard condition. This specimen has been maintained to the highest possible standards, exhibiting an interior and exterior finish that remains indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience that is as precise as it is refined. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a definitive example of automotive excellence.",
